install heml using below link -
https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/


Add Helm - 
helm repo add ingress-nginx \
  https://kubernetes.github.io/ingress-nginx

update repo -
helm repo update

Install ingress using heml chart using nginx-value.yaml file -
helm install my-ing ingress-nginx/ingress-nginx \
  --namespace ingress \
  --version 4.0.17 \
  --values nginx-values.yaml \
  --create-namespace